OL,3,CLarge industrial fire breaks out at
OL,4,CRecycling Centre
OL,6,FEmergency services are responding to a
OL,7,Flarge industrial fire at Llantrisant
OL,8,FRecycling Centre near Pontyclun.
OL,10,FSouth Wales Fire and Rescue Service
OL,11,Fwas called to the incident shortly
OL,12,Fafter 2am following reports of a blaze.
OL,14,FA significant operation is underway,
OL,15,Finvolving eight fire engines, four
OL,16,Fwater bowsers, an aerial ladder
OL,17,Fplatform and a range of specialist
OL,18,Fequipment, including drones.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/3
