OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1784290699
OL,3,CLarge industrial fire breaks out at
OL,4,CRecycling Centre
OL,6,FSouth Wales Fire and Rescue Service is
OL,7,Fworking alongside South Wales Police
OL,8,Fand Public Health Wales to manage the
OL,9,Fincident.
OL,11,FResidents living nearby are being
OL,12,Fadvised to keep their windows and
OL,13,Fdoors closed because of smoke, while
OL,14,Fmembers of the public are urged to
OL,15,Favoid the area to allow emergency
OL,16,Fcrews to work safely.
OL,18,FThe road is currently closed in both
OL,19,Fdirections between Heol y Sarn and
OL,20,FFfordd Pritchard, and the Llantrisant
OL,21,FRoad and Heol Ddu area.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/3
