OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1784290699
OL,3,CLarge industrial fire breaks out at
OL,4,CRecycling Centre
OL,6,FIn a statement, local councillor Sarah
OL,7,FJane Davies said the roads are
OL,8,F"expected to remain closed for some
OL,9,Ftime," and that "updates will be
OL,10,Fprovided by Rhondda Cynon Taf Council
OL,11,Fand Public Health Wales".
OL,13,FThe cause of the fire has not yet been
OL,14,Fconfirmed, and firefighters remain at
OL,15,Fthe scene.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/3
